data.description: Welcome to this adorable farmhouse on 3.97 flat acres! The home includes a soaring wood burning fireplace in the living room and a 2nd fireplace on the lower level, perfect for our chilly winters. 3 large bedrooms plus an office, living room, & family room mean there's a place for everyone. Bring your furry friends, from horses to hamsters. Larger animals can settle right into the 4 stall barn and cross fenced pasture. A large lean-to is perfect for chickens or storage. Equipped with forced air heat and air conditioning. Gated entry to property. Awesome location, close to services and shopping, and less than 7 minutes to either I-5 or the city of Battle Ground.
